cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CR 

The paper proposes a regularization algorithm to train deep neural networks with biased data. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and cryptography and security (cs.CR) since biased data can affect the performance of these fields. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
